<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    
    <head>
        <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/main.css">
        <!-- homepage_layout.css -->
        <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/homepage_style.css">
        <title>Homepage</title>
    </head>
    
    <body>
        <%= erb :header %>
            <main>
                <div style="width: 100%;">
                    <!-- part 1 -->
                    <div class="grid-container">

                        <!-- part1 -->

                        <div class="item1">
                            <img src="imgs/bookingInstruction.png" href="img/bookingInstruction.png">
                        </div>
                        <div class="item2" style="border-right: solid;">
                            <p style="font-size: 2em;">Booking instruction</p>
                            <br>
                            <div style="text-align: left;">

                                <p style="font-size: 1.5em;">Twitter: </p>							
                                <p>Firstly, the booking system is based on Twitter, which can help us to transmit inforamtion More convenient and faster.
                                 So your twitter handle is needed for creating account.</p>
                                <br>
                                <br>

                                <p style="font-size: 1.5em;">interactions : </p>							
                                <p>Then, our team can satisfy the requirements of users by interactions.</p>
                                <br>


                            </div>
                        </div>


                        <!-- part2 -->
                        <div class="item3">
                            <img src="imgs/whyAccount.png" href="img/whyAccount.png">
                        </div>
                        <div class="item4" style="border-right: solid;">
                            <p style="font-size: 2em;">Why you need one account?</p>
                            <br>
                            <div style="text-align: left;">

                                <p style="font-size: 1.5em;">One: </p>
                                <p>You will enjoy the extra benefits provied by our team.</p>
                                <br />

                                <p style="font-size: 1.5em;">Two: </p>
                                <p>Helping user to deal problem easily by the information recorded by account.(Such as ride history.)</p>
                                <br />

                                <p style="font-size: 1.5em;">Three: </p>
                                <P>Saving time of people by helping people to find car which is in the demand of people. ect.</p>
                                <br />

                            </div>
                        </div>


                        <!-- part 3 -->
                        <div class="item5">
                            <img src="imgs/bookingArea.png" href="img/bookingArea.png">
                        </div>
                        <div class="item6">
                            <p style="font-size: 2em;">Car Type</p>
                            <br>
                            <div style="text-align: left;">
                                <p style="font-size: 1.5em;">Standard: </p>
                                <p>It is suitable for 1-3 person.</p>
                                <br />

                                <p style="font-size: 1.5em;">Luxury(better quality): </p>
                                <p>The car model will have better quality, which can provide a more comfortable experience.</p>
                                <br />

                                <P style="font-size: 1.5em;">Mini van (more seats): </p>
                                <p>The car model will have more seats, which is suitable for group activities.</p>
                                <br />

                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>         

                
                <!-- for session logged in -->
                <% if session[:logged_in] %>
                    <p>You are logged in since <%= session[:logged_time].strftime("%d-%m-%Y %H:%M:%S") %></p>
                    <a href="/session_clear">Log Out</a>
                <% end %>
             </main>
         <%= erb :footer %>
